Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.78,0:01:03.40,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.69,0:01:05.00,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,那时候的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.27,0:01:08.18,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,这时候不要说以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:09.82,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不 你说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.47,0:01:47.95,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,为什么要离开自己的岗位 你们想死是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.61,0:01:51.53,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你是哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:53.41,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我是从火星逃出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.55,0:02:19.54,Layzner_Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,760)}成群的杀人机器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:25.36,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,好不容易到达月球 在这里等候我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:31.24,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,只有八个小孩跟一名美军飞行员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:36.20,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,虽然跟之前的机型都不同
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:38.26,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,但能确定是古拉多斯的机动兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:39.62,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,果然是他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:52.00,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,英二 敌人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:54.64,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,新型的机器人接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:57.34,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,果然这里也受到他们攻击了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:02:59.80,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这里也有三架在接近我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:03.09,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,资料信息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:07.65,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,TS-SG-50C 型 「骷髅炮手」 它们的武器有热流弹两门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:07.65,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(610,980)}SKALLGUNNER
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:13.42,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,激光炮一门 内藏式激光 还有自动修理系统
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:34.94,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,最大力量198 最高速度82
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:56.61,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,乔伊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:59.20,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,马卡斯 马卡斯在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:00.14,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我在这
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.85,0:04:06.39,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你们两个带我去驾驶舱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:10.77,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,古雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:16.44,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:17.91,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,当然是作战了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.47,0:04:19.57,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,乔伊 马卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:21.77,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你们两个年纪最大对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:23.22,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你们当我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:27.32,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我没有你们不行 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:29.35,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.49,0:04:34.38,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,古雷特 战斗交给他们两个就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:36.58,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,他们一定会保护我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:37.22,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:40.64,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,可是为了要活下去 我们也要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.09,0:05:53.17,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,大卫 它们是无人战斗机器人 瞄准他们的感应器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:54.03,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.27,0:06:29.18,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,听好了 要看好敌人是否来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:30.62,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:44.14,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,在哪里 敌人在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:45.58,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,还 还没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:49.10,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,来了 在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:06:59.80,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,打到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:01.30,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:04.30,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,还不行 它还在动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:06.34,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:13.87,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你们两个快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:43.45,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,右边 还是左边 哪一边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:45.49,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,在哪边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:48.63,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,下来 古雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:52.66,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,乔伊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:07:59.63,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,来我这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:06.46,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:21.44,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,在哪里 敌人在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:23.48,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,中尉 不要开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:25.74,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,住手 中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:29.20,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,中尉 不要开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:37.24,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白博士 叫中尉停止攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:43.38,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,告诉我 敌人在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:47.02,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,住手 古雷特 你射到同伴了 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:54.94,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,同伴 我射到同伴了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.74,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,够了 已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:00.56,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:18.69,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白博士 趁现在快带孩子们走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:20.42,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:23.74,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,快把大家叫过来 要逃离这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:26.31,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:28.92,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,去我们坐的航天飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:31.60,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,有太空船 太好了 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:38.27,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,把它丢了吧 你眼睛都变成这样了 拿了也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:40.26,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我觉得麻烦时再丢掉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:54.94,Default_Sub_Top,,0,0,0,,罗安 瞄准它的感应器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:57.16,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,射那里的话就可以打倒它了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:10:00.36,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不用你说我也知道瞄那里 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.38,0:11:03.93,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,英二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:39.66,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,八个人 有八个小孩要来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:40.41,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:44.11,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,还有一个美军中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:46.97,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这航天飞机可以容纳这么多人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:49.26,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,可以的 只要把多余的东西丢了就行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:51.48,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,什么是多余的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.98,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,一定是在说你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:11:59.57,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:01.23,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:06.12,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:09.95,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不 我是说那时候的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.77,0:12:13.58,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这时候不要讲以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:15.38,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不 你说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:19.67,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:52.08,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:58.25,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,警告 左前方27号处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:13:00.44,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,有敌人三架侵入
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:14.37,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:15.72,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,英二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:22.06,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:23.56,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,快跟上来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:40.23,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,大家没事吗 跟得上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:41.64,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.37,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,只有他们没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:51.83,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,有我们反而会妨碍他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:06.84,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:09.35,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,紧急生命系统还有用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:20.28,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,大家 可以把头盔拿下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:27.98,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,怎么样 外面的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:29.63,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,没什么改变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:33.95,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,应该被它们压制住了 可以帮我看下外面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:44.80,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,会痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.87,0:14:45.35,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:56.04,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,和那时候一点都没有变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:05.71,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你也一点都没变
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:06.90,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你又看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:08.06,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:11.63,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你的鼻子 嘴唇 眼睛 一切都跟以前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:15.23,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,两边的外眼角各多了一条褶皱 合计多了两条
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:18.72,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,那才好 其实我喜欢年纪较大的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:21.66,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你还是像以前一样不会说话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:23.41,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,听起来好讽刺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:24.26,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:26.74,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,如果可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:30.10,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我们可以再重来一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:34.98,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我想我们两人应该也都又有成长了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:46.18,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,会痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.47,0:15:46.94,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:49.91,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,瞳孔好像没有异状
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:52.42,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,外面的情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:54.90,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,没有异状
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:16:00.66,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,如果只是眼内出血的话花点时间就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:05.77,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,有个好像地下道入口的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:14.26,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,大家 把头盔戴上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:18.15,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,乔伊 减少气压
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:18.62,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:45.14,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,英二 我们在布满缆线的道路上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:47.09,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这里好像连到机场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:49.18,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,应该可以平安到地面上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:49.94,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:52.15,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这样很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:54.82,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这里我们自己会想办法 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:17.93,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你说古拉多斯人 他们是谁 目的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:21.82,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,他们怕地球人侵略宇宙 所以来杀我们地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:25.59,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,好可怕的家伙 竟要杀光地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:31.36,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,那是因为他们害怕四处布兵 想要占领宇宙的地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:35.29,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白 你讨厌我当军人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:39.20,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,可是 你看 不只是地球 宇宙到处都是战争
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:41.41,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,到哪里都避免不了战争
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:43.21,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,军人有其存在的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:46.34,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,就是有你这种想法扭曲了宇宙开发的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.48,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,最后才会招古拉多斯人来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:51.22,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,哼 你还是这么天真
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.53,0:17:52.18,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:59.42,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你一点都没变 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:01.14,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这种话以后都不要再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:11.04,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:12.23,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,没有路了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.38,0:18:14.66,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,找一下有没有岔路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:16.50,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,有了 这好像能上去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:50.74,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这里是哪里 你们知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.14,0:18:52.78,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不知道 我没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:18:59.65,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,那里是机场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:09.88,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:29.19,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,英二 大卫 快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:32.24,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,在哪里 你们在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:35.14,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,外面 在外面 这里是材料存储室
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.76,0:19:37.37,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,从这里看得到机场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:42.34,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,一吸引敌人 就拼命跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:44.74,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:10.90,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,马上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:23.68,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,接着是芙蕾蒂 兰德 弗洛华
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:46.71,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,英二 快来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:48.64,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,在哪里 敌人在上面是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:08.50,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,找到敌人了吗  找到了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:15.83,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这里是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.78,0:21:21.00,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,过来 来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.66,0:21:22.59,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,古雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.64,0:22:29.53,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,走吧 大家 坐那航天飞机回地球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.75,0:22:35.34,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,大家平安上了太空船
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.03,0:22:37.57,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我也松了一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.89,0:22:41.34,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,在经历一连串令人难过的事件后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.15,0:22:44.72,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,能救到这八个小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:49.34,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,也让我们的心中稍微平静 感到开心多了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:56.70,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,警告信息 现况对我方不利 请逃出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.90,0:24:00.78,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,如果这样下去 说不定能知道雷兹纳的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.38,0:24:02.28,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,请逃出
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.22,0:24:04.10,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,让我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.19,0:24:08.45,Layzner_Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs150\pos(720,790)}接下来去地球
